Two Groups May Be Interested in Acquiring Esporta, Times Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-24T01:37:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/two-groups-may-be-interested-in-acquiring-esporta-times-reports.html
  Societe Generale  is believed to be
studying its options after receiving interest in sports club
chain Esporta Plc from two competitors, Virgin Active Ltd. and
David Lloyd Leisure Ltd., the London-based Times reported,
citing people in the industry.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
